title: Brilliant Eze hits hat-trick as Arsenal thump Spurs to extend lead in title race
summary: Eberechi Eze scored a hat-trick as Arsenal defeated Tottenham Hotspur 4-1 in a thrilling north London derby. The victory extends Arsenal's lead at the top of the Premier League to six points. This dominant performance further solidifies Arsenal's title aspirations this season.
